      "predicted_emotion": "neutral",
      "utterance_id": 1,
      "dialog_act": 1
    },
    {
      "text": "Could you tell me how to use it ?",
      "speaker": "S1",
      "predicted_emotion": "neutral",
      "utterance_id": 2,
      "dialog_act": 3
    },
    {
      "text": "You put it in the slot at the turnstile and then push the turnstile to get into the platform .",
      "speaker": "S2",
      "predicted_emotion": "neutral",
      "utterance_id": 3,
      "dialog_act": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Oh , I see . By the way , how can I get out of the platform after I get off the train ?",
      "speaker": "S1",
      "predicted_emotion": "neutral",
      "utterance_id": 4,
      "dialog_act": 2
    },
    {
      "text": "That's very easy . The exit is always open .",
      "speaker": "S2",
      "predicted_emotion": "neutral",
      "utterance_id": 5,
      "dialog_act": 1
    },
    {
      "text": "Thank you for your help .",
